{"tid":446346,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Newsfeed雙軌制】facebook試行專頁帖子唔畀錢會no show","createTime":"2017-10-24T08:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T08:44:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17b83c00a6210a15dd14122fcff1a91d79282c8d","tid":446346,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"facebook越做越大，專頁就越做越難。外媒報道，facebook現正測試「雙軌制」動態時報(newsfeed)，新版動態時報會分拆為二個，主要的動態時報以後只顯示用戶朋友的帖文，與及專頁付費推廣的帖文；致於沒有付費宣傳的專頁帖子，則會被「發配邊疆」，用戶需到另一動態時報才能看到。<br />\n<br />\n有關的測試已於6個地區試行，包括斯洛伐克、塞爾維亞、斯里蘭卡等。據悉專頁的參與度(engagement)下跌介乎六到八成。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook聲明稱，指不斷改動動態時報，以呈現用戶會覺得最有意思的帖文；又稱有用戶反映，希望更容易看到親朋戚友的帖文，所以試行兩個獨立的動態時報，一個顯示親屬朋友帖文，另一個顯示專頁帖文。此外，現時未有計劃將新設定應用於全球其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n然而與聲明不同的是，付費推廣帖文依舊會於主要的動態時報中顯示。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果財經，關心你飯碗<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=HdUXrYEkG2fOkZ1wUI3%2FRE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e1187d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171024/57370518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F57370518&d=HdUXrYEkG2fOkZ1wUI3%2FRE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=6d4a8f3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F57370518&h=3bdf424a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171024/57370518</a>"},{"pid":"5b4404baa0e558a4f963e83d3c329e29444ef711","tid":446346,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T08:34:57.000Z","msg":"咁樣facebook可以玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身page就係要黎接觸public，你玩到唔俾錢就唔俾人你<br />\n即係逼走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4